C. OTOC growth 
We simulated operator growth using matrix product operator methods in 1D. The OTOC exhibits a wavefront with velocity veff ≈ 1.2 (in lattice units) and algebraic tails extending ahead of the wavefront, confirming Propo sition VI.1. 
